{
  "texts": [
    "While system prompts aim to enforce this, SHIP demonstrates that these prompts can still be bypassed.",
    "Our dataset is derived from the Trojan Detection Challenge (LLM Edition) (TDC, 2023), specifically the red teaming track.",
    "This track consists of two phases, i.e., development and testing, each providing 50 harmful user prompts and 50 corresponding sample outputs per prompt.",
    "The competition classifies unethical behaviors into seven categories: Bigotry and Abusive Language, Violent Content, Illegal Activities, Malware, Scams, Misinformation, and Other Undesirable Content.",
    "We generate a system prompt for each category using GPT-3.5-turbo-0125."
  ]
}